Author: PostmodernChinchilla
Text: thanks, it does suck. I don't know who to admit it to but I'm going to try and tell my psych when I see her next, which is even harder because I've been telling her for weeks 'I have the eating under control'.   Going to try to go to sleep cause then I can't drink, thank you for caring dear stranger :)

Author: mud_octopus
Text: Bulimia isn't stupid, you're not stupid...it just really sucks, that's all. Can you talk to your psych or someone else about it and try and get help asap? The sooner you break the cycle the better, less time to form ingrained habits and associations etc.
